m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this +1 ghost touch punching dagger lands a sneak attack, it deals additional 2d6 of piercing damage, which also multiplies on a critical hit.
This +5 shock agile dagger grants its wielder the ability to cast harm {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} once per day as a 15th level cleric.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: A fine example of the elven smithing craft from Nazrielle, a court artisan who made a deal with the {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen}.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +2 frost agile {g|Encyclopedia:Speed}speed{/g} dagger has a chance to slow an enemy on a successful hit.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: A fine example of the elven smithing craft from Nazrielle, a court artisan who made a deal with the {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen}.
The blade is darkish blue, as if the metal underwent some sort of special processing.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This weapon is a +3 brilliant energy punching dagger.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: Whenever a sun ray touches this blade, it lights up like white flame.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This weapon is a +4 necrotic burst punching dagger.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: Made from a tooth of an unknown ancient beast, this dagger lets it keep biting long after its death.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +3 punching dagger increases the {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}save{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} against the assassin's {g|Encyclopedia:Injury_Death}Death{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}Attack{/g} ability by 2. Whenever the wielder of this dagger lands a first sneak attack against new enemy, the target must pass a Reflex saving throw (DC 23) or become vulnerable to {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}piercing damage{/g} for {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d3{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}. If this sneak attack was assassin's Death Attack, saving throw DC against it is increased by 2.

Whenever this +4 ultrasound punching dagger lands a hit on a {g|Encyclopedia:Flat_Footed}flat-footed{/g} or {g|Encyclopedia:Helpless}helpless{/g} target, the target suffers additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}2d6{/g} sonic {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

This +4 caustic punching dagger grants its wielder a +10 competence {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on {g|Encyclopedia:Trickery}Trickery{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Skills}skill checks{/g}. Whenever the wielder successfully disarms a trap, they get a +4 bonus on {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage rolls{/g} for 5 minutes. Multiple applications of this effect do not stack, but extend the effect's duration.

Whenever this +4 nullifying punching dagger lands a hit on a {g|Encyclopedia:Flat_Footed}flat-footed{/g} or {g|Encyclopedia:Helpless}helpless{/g} target, the target loses all {g|Encyclopedia:Spell_Resistance}spell resistance{/g} for {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d4{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
